    <div class="docs-content">
        <h2>Getting Started with SurveySpark</h2>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to start creating and managing surveys with SurveySpark:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Find the "Surveys" section in the navigtation bar and click on it
            </li>
            <li>You will be redirected to a dashboard section and in that secion, 
                click on the "Add Survey" button if you want to create a new survey
            </li>
            <li>Fill in the details of the survey you want to create and click "Create Survey" 
                to create it
            </li>
            <li>
                As you click the button, you will be redirected to the dashboard section 
            </li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Editing and Deleting a Survey</h2>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to edit or delete a survey:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Find the "Surveys" section in the navigtation bar and click on it</li>
            <li>You will be redirected to a dashboard section and in that secion, 
                click on the "Edit" button if you want to edit a survey
            </li>
            <li>Fill in the details of the survey you want to edit and click "Edit Survey" 
                to edit it
            </li>
            <li>As you click the button, you will be redirected to the dashboard section</li>
            <li>Click on the "Delete" button if you want to delete a survey</li>
            <li>Click "Ok" to confirm the deletion</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Taking a Survey</h2>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to take a survey:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Find the " Take Surveys" section in the navigtation bar and click on it
            </li>
            <li>
                You will arrive at the "Take Surveys" page and you will see a list of surveys,
                click on the survey you want to take and click "Take Survey"
            </li>
            <li>
                Fill in the details of the survey you want to take and click "Submit Answers" to submit it
            </li>
        </ul>
